========,1,preface.
Ronneby Municipality ("Ronneby kommun") is a municipality in Blekinge County in southern Sweden.
It borders to Tingsryd Municipality, Emmaboda Municipality, Karlskrona Municipality and Karlshamn Municipality.
The town Ronneby is the seat of the municipality.
The present municipality was created in 1967 through the amalgamation of the "City of Ronneby" with three surrounding units.
